00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:43,960
that enhance the function
of the immune system,

37
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:45,760
and potentially can be used to combat

38
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:47,580
different types of infection.

39
00:01:47,580 --> 00:01:49,650
And just to give you another little hint,

40
00:01:49,650 --> 00:01:53,310
they found that a particular
type of organ tissue

