1840
01:20:23,130 --> 01:20:24,910
I might as well demonstrate it for you

1841
01:20:24,910 --> 01:20:26,160
so you know what this looks like.

1842
01:20:26,160 --> 01:20:29,360
There are variations on
this, so with respect to Wim,

1843
01:20:29,360 --> 01:20:31,120
with respect to Tummo practitioners,

1844
01:20:31,120 --> 01:20:34,150
with respect to the cyclic
hyperventilators everywhere,

1845
01:20:34,150 --> 01:20:36,020
