2264
01:39:34,180 --> 01:39:37,470
And that shouldn't come as a mystery

2265
01:39:37,470 --> 01:39:39,490
or surprise result to us.

2266
01:39:39,490 --> 01:39:42,760
It's because this reward
pathway and the fact

2267
01:39:42,760 --> 01:39:45,220
that it's related to a sense of the future

2268
01:39:45,220 --> 01:39:48,430
seems to liberate entire
systems within the body

2269
01:39:48,430 --> 01:39:52,780
that make inflammatory cytokines go down,

2270
01:39:52,780 --> 01:39:55,610
