2277
01:40:15,443 --> 01:40:17,180
In one case, I'm talking about potentially

2278
01:40:17,180 --> 01:40:20,360
taking an over-the-counter
compound to increase dopamine

2279
01:40:20,360 --> 01:40:21,290
to accelerate healing.

2280
01:40:21,290 --> 01:40:24,380
In another case, we're
talking about using breathing.

2281
01:40:24,380 --> 01:40:27,660
There's also the use
of cold water exposure

2282
01:40:27,660 --> 01:40:28,570
to increase dopamine.

2283
01:40:28,570 --> 01:40:30,300
I talked about this several episodes ago,

2284
01:40:30,300 --> 01:40:33,640
but it's been shown that
immersing oneself in cold water

2285
01:40:33,640 --> 01:40:35,010
up to the neck or so.

2286
01:40:35,010 --> 01:40:35,843
