2302
01:41:17,870 --> 01:41:19,330
increasing neurotransmitter levels,

2303
01:41:19,330 --> 01:41:22,190
that can be done pharmacologically
through supplementation,

2304
01:41:22,190 --> 01:41:24,560
or the can be done
