2343
01:43:09,150 --> 01:43:10,900
So you have to make sure
that you're hydrating well,

2344
01:43:10,900 --> 01:43:13,580
both fluids and electrolytes,

2345
01:43:13,580 --> 01:43:16,840
and they also can interfere with sleep

2346
01:43:16,840 --> 01:43:20,350
because as I've talked about
in the episodes on sleep,

2347
01:43:20,350 --> 01:43:22,710
one of the hallmarks of
deep sleep and in particular

2348
01:43:22,710 --> 01:43:27,310
REM sleep is that epinephrin,
adrenaline levels are low.

2349
01:43:27,310 --> 01:43:29,840
This is what allows you to have intense,

2350
01:43:29,840 --> 01:43:33,770
often very emotionally-laden
dreams during REM sleep

2351
01:43:33,770 --> 01:43:36,370
and not act those out.

2352
01:43:36,370 --> 01:43:40,140
And low adrenaline,
epinephrin during REM sleep

2353
01:43:40,140 --> 01:43:42,230
is basically a signature,

2354
01:43:42,230 --> 01:43:44,330
a neurochemical signature
of the REM sleep state,

2355
01:43:44,330 --> 01:43:47,560
which is so vital for
emotional and physical repair

2356
01:43:47,560 --> 01:43:48,393
and so forth.

2357
01:43:48,393 --> 01:43:50,490
So, the fact that they can inhibit sleep,

2358
01:43:50,490 --> 01:43:52,560
the fact that can cause dehydration,

2359
01:43:52,560 --> 01:43:54,390
the fact that they can make
